1:1 paulov kai timoyeov, douloi ihsou cristou, pasin toiv
 agioiv en cristw ihsou toiv ousin en filippoiv sun episkopoiv
 kai diakonoiv:
1:2 cariv umin kai eirhnh apo yeou patrov hmwn kai kuriou
 ihsou cristou.

1:3 eucaristw tw yew mou epi pash th mneia umwn,
1:4 pantote en pash dehsei mou uper pantwn umwn meta carav
 thn dehsin poioumenov
1:5 epi th koinwnia umwn eiv to euaggelion apo prwthv hmerav
 acri tou nun,
1:6 pepoiywv auto touto, oti o enarxamenov en umin ergon
 agayon epitelesei acri hmerav ihsou cristou,
1:7 kaywv estin dikaion emoi touto fronein uper pantwn umwn
 dia to ecein me en th kardia umav, en te toiv desmoiv mou
 kai en th apologia kai bebaiwsei tou euaggeliou sugkoinwnouv
 mou thv caritov pantav umav ontav.
1:8 martuv gar mou estin o yeov, wv epipoyw pantav umav
 en splagcnoiv ihsou cristou.
1:9 kai touto proseucomai, ina h agaph umwn eti mallon kai
 mallon perisseuh en epignwsei kai pash aisyhsei,
1:10 eiv to dokimazein umav ta diaferonta, ina hte eilikrineiv
 kai aproskopoi eiv hmeran cristou,
1:11 peplhrwmenoi karpwn dikaiosunhv twn dia ihsou cristou
 eiv doxan kai epainon yeou.

1:12 ginwskein de umav boulomai, adelfoi, oti ta kat eme
 mallon eiv prokophn tou euaggeliou elhluyen,
1:13 wste touv desmouv mou fanerouv en cristw genesyai en
 olw tw praitwriw kai toiv loipoiv pasin,
1:14 kai touv pleionav twn adelfwn en kuriw pepoiyotav toiv
 desmoiv mou perissoterwv tolman afobwv ton logon lalein.
1:15 tinev men kai dia fyonon kai erin, tinev de kai di
 eudokian ton criston khrussousin:
1:16 oi men ex eriyeiav ton criston kataggellousin, ouc
 agnwv, oiomenoi yliqin epiferein toiv desmoiv mou:
1:17 oi de ex agaphv, eidotev oti eiv apologian tou euaggeliou
 keimai.
1:18 ti gar; plhn panti tropw, eite profasei eite alhyeia,
 cristov kataggelletai. kai en toutw cairw. alla kai carhsomai:
1:19 oida gar oti touto moi apobhsetai eiv swthrian dia
 thv umwn dehsewv kai epicorhgiav tou pneumatov ihsou cristou,
1:20 kata thn apokaradokian kai elpida mou oti en oudeni
 aiscunyhsomai, all en pash parrhsia, wv pantote, kai nun
 megalunyhsetai cristov en tw swmati mou eite dia zwhv eite
 dia yanatou.
1:21 emoi gar to zhn cristov kai to apoyanein kerdov.
1:22 ei de to zhn en sarki, touto moi karpov ergou, kai
 ti airhsomai ou gnwrizw.
1:23 sunecomai de ek twn duo, thn epiyumian ecwn eiv to
 analusai kai sun cristw einai: pollw [gar] mallon kreisson:
1:24 to de epimenein en th sarki anagkaioteron di umav.
1:25 kai touto pepoiywv oida oti menw kai sumparamenw pasin
 umin eiv thn umwn prokophn kai caran thv pistewv,
1:26 ina to kauchma umwn perisseuh en cristw [ihsou] en emoi
 dia thv emhv parousiav palin prov umav.

1:27 monon axiwv tou euaggeliou tou cristou politeuesye,
 ina eite elywn kai idwn umav eite apwn akousw ta peri umwn,
 oti sthkete en eni pneumati, mia quch sunaylountev th pistei
 tou euaggeliou,
1:28 kai mh pturomenoi en mhdeni upo twn antikeimenwn, htiv
 autoiv men estin endeixiv apwleiav, umin de swthriav, kai
 touto apo yeou:
1:29 oti umin ecarisyh to uper cristou, ou monon to eiv
 auton pisteuein, alla kai to uper autou pascein, --
1:30 ton auton agwna econtev, oion eidete en emoi kai nun
 akouete en emoi.

2:1 ei tiv oun paraklhsiv en cristw, ei ti paramuyion agaphv,
 ei tiv koinwnia pneumatov, ei tiv splagcna kai oiktirmoi,
2:2 plhrwsate mou thn caran, ina to auto fronhte, thn authn
 agaphn econtev, sumqucoi, to en fronountev,
2:3 mhden kata eriyeian h kenodoxian, alla th tapeinofrosunh
 allhlouv hgoumenoi uperecontav eautwn.
2:4 mh ta eautwn ekastov skopeite, alla kai ta eterwn ekastov.
2:5 touto gar froneisyw en umin o kai en cristw ihsou,
2:6 ov en morfh yeou uparcwn ouc arpagmon hghsato to einai
 isa yew,
2:7 all eauton ekenwsen morfhn doulou labwn, en omoiwmati
 anyrwpwn genomenov, 
2:8 kai schmati eureyeiv wv anyrwpov etapeinwsen eauton genomenov
 uphkoov mecri yanatou, yanatou de staurou.
2:9 dio kai o yeov auton uperuqwsen kai ecarisato autw onoma
 to uper pan onoma,
2:10 ina en tw onomati ihsou pan gonu kamqh epouraniwn kai
 epigeiwn kai katacyoniwn,
2:11 kai pasa glwssa exomologhshtai oti kuriov ihsouv cristov
 eiv doxan yeou patrov.

2:12 wste, agaphtoi mou, kaywv pantote uphkousate, mh wv
 en th parousia mou monon, alla nun pollw mallon en th apousia
 mou, meta fobou kai tromou thn eautwn swthrian katergazesye:
2:13 o yeov gar estin o energwn en umin kai to yelein kai
 to energein uper thv eudokiav.
2:14 panta poieite cwriv goggusmwn kai dialogismwn,
2:15 ina genhsye amemptoi kai akeraioi, tekna yeou amwmhta
 en mesw geneav skoliav kai diestrammenhv, en oiv fainesye
 wv fwsthrev en kosmw,
2:16 logon zwhv epecontev, eiv kauchma emoi eiv hmeran cristou,
 oti ouk eiv kenon edramon oude eiv kenon ekopiasa.
2:17 all ei kai spendomai epi th yusia kai leitourgia thv
 pistewv umwn, cairw kai sugcairw pasin umin:
2:18 to d auto kai umeiv cairete kai sugcairete moi.

2:19 elpizw de en kuriw ihsou timoyeon tacewv pemqai umin,
 ina kagw euqucw gnouv ta peri umwn:
2:20 oudena gar ecw isoqucon, ostiv gnhsiwv ta peri umwn
 merimnhsei:
2:21 oi pantev gar ta eautwn zhtousin, ou ta cristou ihsou.
2:22 thn de dokimhn autou ginwskete, oti wv patri teknon
 sun emoi edouleusen eiv to euaggelion.
2:23 touton men oun elpizw pemqai wv an apidw ta peri eme
 exauthv:
2:24 pepoiya de en kuriw oti kai autov tacewv eleusomai.
2:25 anagkaion de hghsamhn epafroditon ton adelfon kai sunergon
 kai sustratiwthn mou, umwn de apostolon kai leitourgon
 thv creiav mou, pemqai prov umav,
2:26 epeidh epipoywn hn pantav umav, kai adhmonwn dioti
 hkousate oti hsyenhsen.
2:27 kai gar hsyenhsen paraplhsion yanatou: all o yeov auton
 hlehsen, ouk auton de monon, alla kai eme, ina mh luphn
 epi luphn scw.
2:28 spoudaioterwv oun epemqa auton, ina idontev auton palin
 carhte, kagw alupoterov w.
2:29 prosdecesye oun auton en kuriw meta pashv carav, kai
 touv toioutouv entimouv ecete,
2:30 oti dia to ergon tou cristou mecri yanatou hggisen,
 parabouleusamenov th quch ina anaplhrwsh to umwn usterhma
 thv prov me leitourgiav.

3:1 to loipon, adelfoi mou, cairete en kuriw. ta auta grafein
 umin emoi men ouk oknhron, umin de asfalev.
3:2 blepete touv kunav, blepete touv kakouv ergatav, blepete
 thn katatomhn:
3:3 hmeiv gar esmen h peritomh, oi pneumati yeou latreuontev
 kai kaucwmenoi en cristw ihsou kai ouk en sarki pepoiyotev,
3:4 kaiper egw ecwn pepoiyhsin kai en sarki. ei tiv dokei
 allov pepoiyenai en sarki, egw mallon:
3:5 peritomh oktahmerov, ek genouv israhl, fulhv beniamin,
 ebraiov ex ebraiwn, kata nomon farisaiov,
3:6 kata zhlon diwkwn thn ekklhsian, kata dikaiosunhn thn
 en nomw genomenov amemptov.
3:7 all atina hn moi kerdh, tauta hghmai dia ton criston
 zhmian.
3:8 alla menounge kai hgoumai panta zhmian einai dia to
 uperecon thv gnwsewv cristou ihsou tou kuriou mou, di on
 ta panta ezhmiwyhn, kai hgoumai skubala einai ina criston
 kerdhsw
3:9 kai eureyw en autw mh ecwn emhn dikaiosunhn thn ek nomou,
 alla thn dia pistewv cristou, thn ek yeou dikaiosunhn epi
 th pistei,
3:10 tou gnwnai auton kai thn dunamin thv anastasewv autou
 kai thn koinwnian twn payhmatwn autou, summorfoumenov tw
 yanatw autou,
3:11 ei pwv katanthsw eiv thn exanastasin twn nekrwn.
3:12 ouc oti hdh elabon h hdh teteleiwmai, diwkw de ei kai
 katalabw, ef w kai katelhfyhn upo tou cristou ihsou.
3:13 adelfoi, egw emauton oupw logizomai kateilhfenai: en
 de, ta men opisw epilanyanomenov toiv de emprosyen epekteinomenov
3:14 kata skopon diwkw epi to brabeion thv anw klhsewv tou
 yeou en cristw ihsou.
3:15 osoi oun teleioi, touto fronwmen: kai ei ti eterwv
 froneite, kai touto o yeov umin apokaluqei.
3:16 plhn eiv o efyasamen, tw autw stoicein kanoni, to auto
 fronein.

3:17 summimhtai mou ginesye, adelfoi, kai skopeite touv
 outwv peripatountav, kaywv ecete tupon hmav.
3:18 polloi gar peripatousin, -- ouv pollakiv elegon umin,
 nun de kai klaiwn legw, touv ecyrouv tou staurou tou cristou,
3:19 wn to telov apwleia, wn o yeov h koilia kai h doxa
 en th aiscunh autwn, oi ta epigeia fronountev!
3:20 hmwn gar to politeuma en ouranoiv uparcei, ex ou kai
 swthra apekdecomeya kurion ihsoun criston,
3:21 ov metaschmatisei to swma thv tapeinwsewv hmwn eiv
 to genesyai auto summorfon tw swmati thv doxhv autou kata
 thn energeian tou dunasyai auton kai upotaxai autw ta panta.

4:1 wste, adelfoi mou agaphtoi kai epipoyhtoi, cara kai
 stefanov mou, outwv sthkete en kuriw, agaphtoi.

4:2 euodian parakalw kai suntuchn parakalw to auto fronein
 en kuriw:
4:3 nai erwtw kai se, suzuge gnhsie, sullambanou autaiv,
 aitinev en tw euaggeliw sunhylhsan moi meta kai klhmentov
 kai twn loipwn sunergwn mou, wn ta onomata en biblw zwhv.

4:4 cairete en kuriw pantote: palin erw, cairete.
4:5 to epieikev umwn gnwsyhtw pasin anyrwpoiv. o kuriov
 egguv.
4:6 mhden merimnate, all en panti th proseuch kai th dehsei
 meta eucaristiav ta aithmata umwn gnwrizesyw prov ton yeon.
4:7 kai h eirhnh tou yeou h uperecousa panta noun frourhsei
 tav kardiav umwn kai ta nohmata umwn en cristw ihsou.

4:8 to loipon, adelfoi, osa estin alhyh, osa semna, osa
 dikaia, osa agna, osa prosfilh, osa eufhma, ei tiv areth
 kai ei tiv epainov, tauta logizesye:
4:9 a kai emayete kai parelabete kai hkousate kai eidete
 en emoi, tauta prassete: kai o yeov thv eirhnhv estai mey
 umwn.

4:10 ecarhn de en kuriw megalwv oti hdh pote aneyalete to
 uper emou fronein: ef w kai efroneite, hkaireisye de.
4:11 ouc oti kay usterhsin legw: egw gar emayon en oiv eimi
 autarkhv einai.
4:12 oida kai tapeinousyai, oida kai perisseuein: en panti
 kai en pasin memuhmai kai cortazesyai kai peinan, kai perisseuein
 kai ustereisyai:
4:13 panta iscuw en tw endunamounti me cristw.
4:14 plhn kalwv epoihsate sugkoinwnhsantev mou th yliqei.
4:15 oidate de kai umeiv, filipphsioi, oti en arch tou euaggeliou,
 ote exhlyon apo makedoniav, oudemia moi ekklhsia ekoinwnhsen
 eiv logon dosewv kai lhqewv ei mh umeiv monoi,
4:16 oti kai en yessalonikh kai apax kai div eiv thn creian
 moi epemqate.
4:17 ouc oti epizhtw to doma, all epizhtw ton karpon ton
 pleonazonta eiv logon umwn.
4:18 apecw de panta kai perisseuw: peplhrwmai dexamenov
 para epafroditou ta par umwn, osmhn euwdiav, yusian dekthn,
 euareston tw yew.
4:19 o de yeov mou plhrwsei pasan creian umwn kata ton plouton
 autou en doxh en cristw ihsou.
4:20 tw de yew kai patri hmwn h doxa eiv touv aiwnav twn
 aiwnwn: amhn.

4:21 aspasasye panta agion en cristw ihsou. aspazontai umav
 oi sun emoi adelfoi.
4:22 aspazontai umav pantev oi agioi, malista de oi ek thv
 kaisarov oikiav.

4:23 h cariv tou kuriou ihsou cristou meta pantwn umwn:
 amhn.
